{
  "info": {
    "name": "Security Agency Management System API - Dynamic Auth",
    "description": "Complete REST API with Dynamic User Authentication\n\nBase URL: http://localhost:3000/api/v1\n\nAuthentication: Bearer Token (JWT)\n\nUser Roles:\n- DIRECTOR: Full system access (can manage users, all operations)\n- ADMIN: Can manage guards, tenders, attendance, reports\n- SUPERVISOR: View and mark attendance for their zone only\n\nWorkflow:\n1. First user registered automatically becomes DIRECTOR\n2. Director can create ADMIN and SUPERVISOR users\n3. All users login with username/email and password\n4. JWT token expires after 8 hours\n\nDefault Admin (auto-created if no users exist):\n- Username: admin\n- Password: admin123\n- Email: admin@securityagency.com",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "version": "2.0.0"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:3000/api/v1",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "userId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "guardId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "supervisorId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "tenderId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "attendanceId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "salaryId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "1. Authentication & User Management",
      "description": "Dynamic user authentication and management endpoints",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "1.1 Register First User (Auto becomes DIRECTOR)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (jsonData.access_token) {",
                  "    pm.environment.set(\"token\", jsonData.access_token);",
                  "    pm.environment.set(\"userId\", jsonData.user.id);",
                  "    console.log(\"Token saved successfully\");",
                  "}",
                  "pm.test(\"Status code is 200 or 201\", function () {",
                  "    pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.be.oneOf([200, 201]);",
                  "});",
                  "pm.test(\"Response has access_token\", function () {",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property(\"access_token\");",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n    \"fullName\": \"System Administrator\",\n    \"email\": \"admin@securityagency.com\",\n    \"username\": \"admin\",\n    \"password\": \"admin123\",\n    \"mobileNumber\": \"9999999999\",\n    \"role\": \"director\",\n    \"zoneName\": \"Head Office\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/register",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "register"]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
